com.austinv11.collectiveframework.utils.security

Class Encryption.EncryptionType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.austinv11.collectiveframework.utils.security.Encryption.EncryptionType
  • Enclosing class:
    Encryption

    public static final class Encryption.EncryptionType
extends java.lang.Object
    Eases the management of algorithms, modes, and padding See http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/technotes/guides/security/StandardNames.html#Cipher for a description of each. Use this in the place of a string for encryption types.
